title: [P3Dv2-FSX] Majestic Q400 1.011 PILOT UNCRACKED
description:
The MJC8 Q400 addon for Microsoft Flight Simulator X and Lockheed Martin Prepar3d v2 is a highly realistic rendition, built after the Bombardier (tm) Dash8 Q400 aircraft. 


"PILOT" is an edition, designed for home flightsimmers, who want a state-of-the-art hardcore add-on but do not require the complex features, such as the instructor panel system monitoring, circuit breakers simulation, failures simulation, or the shared cockpit.


System requirements: Any PC capable of running Flight Simulator.

Supported versions: Microsoft FSX Service Pack 2 or Acceleration / Lockheed Martin Prepar3d v2.2 and higher
